    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "That's too bad. ._. Would it be possible to define the sorting manually, though? Aside from the 4 options (count|isRefined|name:asc|name:desc)? I need this sorting: Fachbereich / Zentren / Experten / Sprechstunden\r\n\r\nI had my PHP indexer run in this order, but as soon as the items are imported, Algolia just ignores this order.",
